LD37 Brainstorming
=============================
Theme = "One Room"

***Ideas***
-Uses basic colors and shapes
-Maze type game
-You see the entire map at the beginning, before you can only see a small portion around yourself
-There is a light power up that shows you the map again for a brief moment
-There are some monsters that move back and forth
-There are hidden traps that are only seen when the whole map is lit up
-You are given a rank based on your time of completion

***What to do on Saturday Morning***
-Finish Core Game:
	+Add enemies and traps
	+Add a start and end to a level
-Start Polishing
-Link Levels Together